name: DEEP SLEEP PEEL SPEED DEEPS LEEP PEELS PEED
description: I began to experiment combining words that are seemingly nonsensical to see what would happen. In the title, we have two different ways to interpret the same lines. Both have 4 words that are valid spelled backwards and forwards. English is a strange, strange muse that never ceases to give and give. Which is the version to read it as correct. The answer is both. Why not?
